> Hi Dan,
> We wrote an article for the type2 library on this subject.  The 72 and
later
> dual circuit MC has the same bore diameter as the 1955-67 MCs.  The only
> change is a longer bore for the front disc brakes which required more CCs
of
> brake fluid, which does not affect braking power in drum brakes.
> Eric&Barb
